chunks.html_content:
Use this service to check:

  • if a UK VAT registration number is valid
  • the name and address of the business the number is registered to
chunks.plain_content:
Check a UK VAT number
Use this service to check:

  if a UK VAT registration number is valid
  the name and address of the business the number is registered to

chunks.html_content: This service is also available in Welsh (Cymraeg).
chunks.plain_content:
Check a UK VAT number
This service is also available in Welsh (Cymraeg).

chunks.html_content: If you are a UK VAT-registered business, you can also use this service to prove when you checked a UK VAT number. You will need your own VAT number to do this.
chunks.plain_content:
Check a UK VAT number
If you are a UK VAT-registered business, you can also use this service to prove when you checked a UK VAT number. You will need your own VAT number to do this.

chunks.html_content: You cannot use this service if you’ve already applied to register for VAT and you’re waiting to hear back from HMRC. Check when you should expect a reply.
chunks.plain_content:
